            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 14:00:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Borderlands 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Civilization VII]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mafia: The Old Country]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TGA 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Witcher 4]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281327</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今日舉行的 2024 年遊戲大獎（The Game Awards）中，除了讓人回顧今年的優秀遊戲外，遊戲廠商也趁機會公佈大作，其中《巫師》、《邊緣禁地》、《四海兄弟》和《文明帝國》的最新續作也有全新預告片公開。<br /><span id="more-1281327"></span></p><h2>《巫師 4》(The Witcher 4)</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51092"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/54dabgZJ5YA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>今次公開的是《巫師 4》首個預告片，雖然沒有實際遊戲畫面，但也預告了遊戲故事內容，預告中主角不再是傑洛特 (Geralt) 而是他的養女希裏 (Ciri)，她在偏遠村莊接下獵魔士委託，面對需要人類獻祭的邪惡生物。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202419-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202419-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202419-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202441-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202441-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4thegameawards202441-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在村民準備獻祭年輕女孩時希裏挺身而出，卻發現自己陷入與村民的偏見和迷信的衝突中。遊戲採用虛幻引擎 5 製作，預計成為系列新三部曲的首作，不過發行時間就尚未公佈。</p><h2>《邊緣禁地 4》(Borderlands 4)</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69255"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/R8CaRnf0zO0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>《邊緣禁地 4》預告片則揭露全新反派「時域天尊」(The Timekeeper)，以及最危險星球凱羅星 (Kairos) 上的冒險。遊戲將提供傳統全新寶庫獵人技能樹系統，新的探索機制，以及可自由召喚載具的功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281334" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/borderlands4firstloo-1-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>製作人 Randy Pitchford 表示，這將是系列最瘋狂的作品，提供前所未有的武器系統和難忘的劇情。遊戲支援單人遊玩或與最多三名玩家合作，預計 2025 年推出。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
