        <item>
            <title>【TGA 2024】《鬼武者 Way of the Sword》終於登場，延續爽快遊戲體驗</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/onimusha-way-of-the-sword/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=onimusha-way-of-the-sword</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/13/onimusha-way-of-the-sword/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 10:31:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[鬼武者]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281273</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今日的「The Game Awards 2024」頒獎典禮上，CAPCOM 發表了「鬼武者」系列全新作品《鬼武者 Way of the Sword》，延續系列標誌性的劍鬥動作玩法。<br /><span id="more-1281273"></span></p><p>在 2001 年推出的《鬼武者》當初推出的時候除了以爽快的日本武士動作玩法為賣點，更找來金城武擔任臉模和配音，引起不少話題，之後的第二和第三集都相當受歡迎，但第四集則一直未有消息。Netflix 去年推出改編版的「鬼武者」動畫作品，令玩家再次想起這經典遊戲，最近 Capcom 終於時隔 20 年公佈全新作品《鬼武者 Way of the Sword》，滿足玩家的期待。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51952"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/la0NtENnuf8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>新作背景設定在江户時代初期的京都，玩家將扮演一位配戴「鬼之籠手」的武士，在籠罩著瘴氣的詭異京都中，與來自異界的幻魔展開激烈戰鬥。從預告片中可以看到新作固然發揮了次世代主機的高畫質，令詭異和風世界觀更加有沉浸感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281290" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0003-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281291" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0006-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0006-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0006-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281292" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0010-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0018-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0018-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0018-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281294" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0011-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0011-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0011-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281295" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0009-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0009-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0009-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《鬼武者 Way of the Sword》預計在 2026 年在 PlayStation 5、 Xbox Series X|S 和 Steam 平台發售，目前遊戲的詳細故事、角色和玩法都未有太多消息，有待進一步的公佈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281296" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0002-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281297" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0019-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0019-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0019-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281298" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0014-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0014-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ps0014-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>來源：新聞稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
